{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "06", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "14", "S": "11"}}, "news": [{"title": "About 170 vacant site owners in Trichy get notices for poor upkeep", "para": "Trichy Corporation is actively identifying and issuing notices to owners of poorly maintained vacant plots, warning them to clear overgrown weeds and level the ground to prevent water stagnation.  So far, 170 notices have been served, with owners given a grace period to comply or face penalties and charges for cleaning.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/trichy-corporation-issues-170-notices-to-owners-of-poorly-maintained-vacant-sites/125123332?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189632/125123332.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Ghaziabad: GDA set to seek objections before acquiring land for Indirapuram extension", "para": "Ghaziabad Development Authority will now seek public objections for land acquisition for its Indirapuram Extension scheme following an Allahabad High Court order. The court directed GDA to pay up to twice the 2014 circle rate to 35 farmers for 153 acres of unacquired land, after a prolonged legal battle spanning over 18 years.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/gda-to-seek-public-objections-for-land-acquisition-in-indirapuram-extension-scheme/125123189?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-20288/125123189.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Stamp registration services to pause in Noida & Ghaziabad between Nov 8-11 for server migration", "para": "Property registrations in Noida and Ghaziabad will be suspended from November 8 to 11 due to a server migration to the National Govt Cloud. This temporary halt aims to enhance system efficiency and data security, though it is expected to cause a significant revenue dip for the state exchequer.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/noida-ghaziabad-to-suspend-property-registrations-for-server-migration-from-nov-8-11/125123061?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-27580/125123061.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}